1 WHEREAS, in recognition of his extraordinary contributions to the university and
2 to the sport of basketball, the playing court at Prather Coliseum was officially named in his
3 honor on February 15, 2025; and
4 WHEREAS, he has been inducted into the Louisiana Tech Athletic Hall of Fame, the
5 Northwestern State Athletic Hall of Fame, the Ark-La-Tex Museum of Champions, and the
6 Northwestern State Hall of Distinguished Educators; and
7 WHEREAS, through his leadership, perseverance, and lifelong commitment to
8 excellence, Mike McConathy has left an indelible mark on collegiate athletics in Louisiana.
9 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Legislature of Louisiana does hereby
10 commend Mike McConathy on being inducted into the 2026 class of the Louisiana Sports
11 Hall of Fame.
12 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to Mike
13 McConathy.
